ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of BRAM ABRAMSON of Toronto, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and his designation for the Ontario region, effective February 15, 2023.
